    <item>
     <widget class="QLabel" name="grades35_lbl">
      <property name="text">
       <string>If in the future I ask you the question too soon, and you're able to remember it without any effort, you rate the card a 5. I'll take this into account by waiting a lot longer before asking you this question again.

If I get it just right, so that you remember it, albeit with some effort, you use grade 4.

If on the other hand it takes you significant effort to remember the answer, and you think I've waited too long to ask you this question, then rate the card 3.

If you fail to remember it altogether, rate it either 0 or 1, and I'll keep on asking you this question until you think you'll be able to remember it again for a few days.</string>
